  "text": "The effect of the up-and downregulated miRNAs was calculated separately as described by [CITATION_1] ; however, we combined the two lists into one by adding the inhibitory effect of the upregulated miRNAs with the stabilising effect of the downregulated miRNAs. We used a cutoff on our weighted inhibitor score list of ±2, resulting in 497 genes that were used for the biological function and pathway analyses in Ingenuity system software.",
